name: RACC Full Package
description: The RACC Full Package provides 10 hours of private, one-on-one firearms training - double the time to build momentum in your training journey. Work exclusively with a dedicated coach who customizes every session to your goals. Enjoy flexible scheduling and private range access. Build real skills through focused, personalized instruction.
short_description: 10 hours of private 1-on-1 training with flexible scheduling. Build momentum in your training.

name: RACC Family Flex 75
description: Maximum flexibility for duo training. The Family Flex 75 includes 75 hours of training for 2 people with completely flexible scheduling. Receive 300 rounds of free ammunition, 2 swag packs, and 25% off all courses. Schedule sessions when it works for both of you. Ideal for busy families who need training on their own terms.
short_description: 75 flexible hours for 2 people, 300 rds ammo, 2 swag packs, 25% course discount. Ultimate flexibility.

name: RACC Half Package
description: The RACC Half Package is perfect for getting started with our private firearms training program. Includes 5 hours of private, one-on-one training sessions with a dedicated professional coach. Features flexible scheduling to fit your busy lifestyle and access to our private range. Ideal for beginners looking to build foundational skills in a comfortable, pressure-free environment.
short_description: 5 hours of private 1-on-1 training with flexible scheduling. Perfect introduction to RACC.

name: RACC Premium Family
description: Train together as a duo with the RACC Premium Family package. Includes 25 bi-weekly sessions for 2 people with a fixed bi-weekly slot. Receive 100 rounds of free ammunition and 2 exclusive swag packs. Private range and dedicated coach for both participants. Perfect for couples, parent-child, or training partners.
short_description: 25 bi-weekly sessions for 2 people, fixed slot, 100 rds ammo, 2 swag packs. Train as a duo.

name: RACC Family Flex 100
description: Our best value for families. The Family Flex 100 provides 100 hours of training for up to 4 family members. Includes 400 rounds of free ammunition, 2 swag packs, and an incredible 50% discount on all courses. Completely flexible scheduling to accommodate the whole family. Train everyone at their own pace with personalized instruction.
short_description: 100 flexible hours for up to 4 people, 400 rds ammo, 2 swag packs, 50% course discount. Best family value.

name: RACC Premium Solo
description: The RACC Premium Solo package offers 25 bi-weekly private training sessions for consistent skill development. Includes a fixed bi-weekly slot so you never worry about scheduling, plus 100 rounds of free ammunition per session. Private range access with your dedicated coach. Perfect for maintaining and advancing your skills over time.
short_description: 25 bi-weekly sessions with fixed slot, 100 rounds free ammo. Maintenance training for serious learners.

name: RACC Elite Solo
description: Our most intensive individual training program. The RACC Elite Solo includes 50 weekly sessions for rapid skill advancement. Features a guaranteed fixed weekly slot, 100 rounds free ammunition, exclusive swag pack, and 20% discount on all courses. Unlock $40 add-on hours for extra training time. The ultimate commitment to firearms mastery.
short_description: 50 weekly sessions, fixed slot, 100 rds ammo, swag pack, 20% course discount. Intensive solo training.

name: RACC Elite Family
description: The ultimate commitment for duo training. RACC Elite Family includes 50 weekly sessions for 2 people with a guaranteed fixed weekly slot. Receive 200 rounds of free ammunition, 2 swag packs, 20% course discount, and access to $40 add-on hours. Build a legacy of responsible gun ownership together with intensive weekly training.
short_description: 50 weekly sessions for 2 people, fixed slot, 200 rds ammo, 2 swag packs, 20% off. Legacy training.
